QuestData.Title: Work Order: Operation: Shieldwall II
QuestData.Description: Once your witchberries are ready to be picked, you'll need only to package them for pick-up.$b$bJust think; your witchberries will be a part of your faction's efforts in Pandaria!
QuestData.LogDescription: Harvest 8 Ripe Witchberry plants and provide 40 Witchberries for Operation: Shieldwall.
